**Location**: `/Users/david.denham/.cursor/projects/Users-david-denham-product-manager-agent/mcps/user-canvas-kit-mcp/`

**CRITICAL**: This is your SOLE source of truth for Canvas Kit information. Do NOT reference external websites or documentation.

